title: Hackathon Signup Open!
content: Hey Winfo Members! Here is the google doc to sign up for the 12th annual WINFO Hackathon! Spots fill up fast so be sure to grab yours. This years theme is 'Endless Possibilities, Endless Solutions'. For more questions about the event feel free to email us at winfo@uw.edu or find us on instagram! https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfTaQFwTOuNHhjR1-5pc4GmPOByVm-kldlaJKsAwsS2WaHgZw/closedform
